{"data":[{"id":563667762,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563667762","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546263570,"updated_time":1546263570,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"comment_count":56,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e看到这个问题已经是1月1日的最后一天了，希望题主能看见吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e作为同龄人，且文科生，我不了解哥猜有多重要有多难以证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于像其他高票回答里说清北配不上你。我想在此总结一下他们的逻辑链：为了上清北→证明哥猜→方法投机取巧难度大→题主狭隘→不可能证明哥猜。个人感觉不太说的通。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主想证明哥猜的功利性未必像高票回答说的那样强。因为兴趣，所以巧合证明出了哥猜。而不知道哥猜的难度和深度，所以抛出了这样一个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可以说题主格局确实有点狭隘，但这不妨碍人家证明哥猜啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外对于高票回答所说，没有看过别人的论文就一定证明不出哥猜。按照我十分浅薄的理解，我认为，世界上第一个发现关于某专业领域专业知识的人，他可以看谁的论文呢?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有一些高票回答说，专业领域的人的解不出来，高中生怎么可能。这也不排除高手在民间啊不是吗。某些答主的格局可能也比较狭隘吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只是通过我狭隘有限的对数学的认识认为，高中生证明出哥猜，有这个可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e会不会被清北录取，一定会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e梦想还是要有的。但是如果失败的话，建议还是踏实学习吧。热爱是动力，但不是唯一。如果真的喜欢数学，不如以此为契机考个好大学深造。即使现在证明不了哥猜不代表深造之后不能。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"看到这个问题已经是1月1日的最后一天了，希望题主能看见吧。作为同龄人，且文科生，我不了解哥猜有多重要有多难以证明。对于像其他高票回答里说清北配不上你。我想在此总结一下他们的逻辑链：为了上清北→证明哥猜→方法投机取巧难度大→题主狭隘→不可能证…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=2185\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bd